  "verdict": "Structural signals beat the past-churn null: keeping complexity/sprawl/public raises pooled leave-one-repo-out AUC by \u0394=+0.086 over activity alone. They carry maintenance-burden signal beyond 'active code stays active.' The file-line sprawl half remains net-noise under this outcome (coef +0.039, 95% CI [-0.046, 0.162]). Analysis only; no weight change. Change-proneness is a proxy (got-edited, not was-painful), the corpus is a gradient toward \u2014 not at \u2014 the AI-side-project target, and the construct gap (edits != maintainability) is anchored, not closed, by the review-comment check."
